{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "sec1-a1b2-c3d4-e5f6-789012345678",
    "name": "KOMANDs Security Tests v1.0",
    "description": "## Suite T7 — Seguridad OWASP ASVS\n\nPruebas de seguridad contra el servidor DEV KOMANDs. Cubre:\n\n| Código | Área |\n|--------|------|\n| TC-SEC-AUTH | Validación JWT (algoritmo, expiración, manipulación) |\n| TC-SEC-HDR | Headers obligatorios |\n| TC-SEC-MTH | Métodos HTTP no permitidos |\n| TC-SEC-RES | Headers de seguridad en respuesta |\n\n**Prerequisito:** Entorno `KOMANDs DEV` activo. SSL verification OFF.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "var token = pm.collectionVariables.get('access_token');",
          "var expiry = parseInt(pm.collectionVariables.get('token_expiry') || '0');",
          "var now = Date.now();",
          "if (!token || now >= expiry) {",
          "    var base_url = pm.environment.get('base_url') || pm.collectionVariables.get('base_url');",
          "    var client_id = pm.environment.get('client_id') || pm.collectionVariables.get('client_id');",
          "    var client_secret = pm.environment.get('client_secret') || pm.collectionVariables.get('client_secret');",
          "    var scope = pm.environment.get('scope') || pm.collectionVariables.get('scope');",
          "    pm.sendRequest({",
          "        url: base_url + '/api/Komands/v1/auth/token',",
          "        method: 'POST',",
          "        header: { 'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded' },",
          "        body: {",
          "            mode: 'urlencoded',",
          "            urlencoded: [",
          "                { key: 'grant_type', value: 'client_credentials' },",
          "                { key: 'client_id', value: client_id },",
          "                { key: 'client_secret', value: client_secret },",
          "                { key: 'scope', value: scope }",
          "            ]",
          "        }",
          "    }, function(err, res) {",
          "        if (!err && res.code === 200) {",
          "            var body = res.json();",
          "            pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', body.access_token);",
          "            var expiresIn = body.expires_in || 3600;",
          "            pm.collectionVariables.set('token_expiry', String(Date.now() + (expiresIn - 60) * 1000));",
          "        }",
          "    });",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{access_token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "TC-SEC-AUTH — Autenticación JWT",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "TC-SEC-AUTH-01 Sin Authorization header",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('TC-SEC-AUTH-01: Sin token → acceso denegado (401/403)', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([401, 403]);",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('[HALLAZGO RFC-7235] Servidor debería retornar 401 (no 403) para credenciales ausentes', function() {",
                  "    if (pm.response.code === 403) {",
                  "        console.warn('HALLAZGO: RFC 7235 §3.1 exige HTTP 401 cuando faltan credenciales. El servidor retorna 403. Reportar al equipo de desarrollo.');",
                  "    }",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([401, 403]);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "X-Source-System", "value": "SN" },
              { "key": "X-Correlation-ID", "value": "{{$guid}}" },
              { "key": "X-Source-System-ID", "value": "abc123def4567890abcdef0123456789" },
              { "key": "X-User-ID", "value": "sec-tester" },
              { "key": "X-User-Role", "value": "agent" },
              { "key": "X-User-Organization", "value": "ON-NET CHILE" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/Komands/v1/query-access/{{test_olt_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "Komands", "v1", "query-access", "{{test_olt_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "ESCENARIO: Petición sin header Authorization.\nRESULTADO ESPERADO: HTTP 401 Unauthorized."
          },
          "response": []
        },
